{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_014YCubmwUPXejrpDsU1QYsW","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01GY7cqnfJyMNU4xCHt3RoTx","name":"Task","input":{"subagent_type":"Explore","description":"Explore Lord of RNGs frontend UI","prompt":"I need to understand the Lord of the RNGs frontend components for writing E2E tests. I need CSS class selectors and the UI flow. Read these files thoroughly:\n\n1. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/lord-of-rngs/LordOfRngsPage.tsx` - main page component\n2. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/lord-of-rngs/components/TierLobby.tsx` - tier lobby\n3. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/lord-of-rngs/components/ActiveRoundView.tsx` - active round view\n4. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/lord-of-rngs/components/WheelVisualization.tsx` - wheel viz\n5. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/lord-of-rngs/components/TierRoundView.tsx` - tier round card\n6. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/lord-of-rngs/types.ts` - types\n7. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/lord-of-rngs/context/LordOfRngsContext.tsx` - context\n\nFor each component, I need:\n- All CSS class names used (lord-* or lotr-* or similar patterns)\n- What elements are rendered in what states\n- Button labels and action handlers\n- How the user flow works: tier selection → join → countdown → spin → claim\n\nBe extremely thorough. Report ALL CSS classes you find."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":8449,"cache_read_input_tokens":72126,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":8449},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3430a832-47ac-41dd-bbc6-e4b8a98508e0","uuid":"1d219ff1-c0d5-46cb-87c8-3bb8ee1806e7"}
