by__grid                - Grid of tier cards\nlotr-tier-card                       - Single tier card button\nlotr-tier-card--waiting              - Phase modifier (waiting state)\nlotr-tier-card--countdown            - Phase modifier (countdown state)\nlotr-tier-card--spinning             - Phase modifier (spinning state)\nlotr-tier-card--complete             - Phase modifier (complete state)\nlotr-tier-card--selected             - Selected state modifier\nlotr-tier-card__header               - Card header section\nlotr-tier-card__name                 - Tier name (iron/bronze/silver/gold/platinum/diamond)\nlotr-tier-card__amount               - Entry amount in SOL\nlotr-tier-card__stats                - Stats section container\nlotr-tier-card__stat                 - Individual stat block\nlotr-tier-card__stat-label           - Stat label (Players/Pool/Entries)\nlotr-tier-card__stat-value           - Stat numeric value\nlotr-tier-card__phase                - Phase indicator section\nlotr-tier-card__phase-text           - Phase text label\nrng-tier-gem                         - Tier gem icon\nrng-tier-gem--iron                   - Iron tier gem\nrng-tier-gem--bronze                 - Bronze tier gem\nrng-tier-gem--silver                 - Silver tier gem\nrng-tier-gem--gold                   - Gold tier gem\nrng-tier-gem--platinum               - Platinum tier gem\nrng-tier-gem--diamond                - Diamond tier gem\n```\n\n### Active Round View\n\n```\nlotr-active-round                    - Active round container\nlotr-active-round--waiting           - Phase modifier (waiting)\nlotr-active-round--countdown         - Phase modifier (countdown)\nlotr-active-round--spinning          - Phase modifier (spinning)\nlotr-active-round--revealing         - Phase modifier (revealing)\nlotr-active-round--complete          - Phase modifier (complete)\nlotr-active-round__phase             - Phase display section\nlotr-active-round__phase-message     - Phase message text\nlotr-active-round__wheel             - Wheel container\nlotr-tier-round__back                - Back button\n```\n\n### Tier Round View\n\n```\nlotr-tier-round                      - Tier round view container\nlotr-tier-round__back                - Back to tiers button\nlotr-tier-round__phase               - Phase indicator section\nlotr-tier-round__phase-message       - Phase message text\nlotr-tier-round__wheel               - Wheel container\nlotr-tier-round__empty-wheel         - Empty wheel placeholder\nlotr-tier-round__empty-wheel-circle  - Empty wheel circle\nlotr-tier-round__empty-wheel-hint    - Empty wheel hint text\n```\n\n### Countdown Timer\n\n```\nlotr-countdown                       - Countdown timer container\nlotr-countdown--small                - Small size modifier\nlotr-countdown--large                - Large size modifier\nlotr-countdown--urgent               - Urgent state (<=10 seconds)\nlotr-countdown--final                - Final countdown (<=5 seconds)\nlotr-countdown__time                 - Time display (MM:SS)\nlotr-countdown__label                - \"until reveal\" label\n```\n\n### Wheel Visualization\n\n```\nlotr-hwheel                          - Wheel container\nlotr-hwheel__indicator               - Golden arrow indicator\nlotr-hwheel__indicator-label         - \"THE ONE\" label above arrow\nlotr-hwheel__indicator-arrow         - Arrow SVG container\nlotr-hwheel__container               - Visible wheel viewport\nlotr-hwheel__strip                   - Infinite scroll strip\nlotr-hwheel__slot                    - Individual slot\nlotr-hwheel__slot--empty             - Empty/placeholder slot\nlotr-hwheel__slot--you               - Current user's slot\nlotr-hwheel__slot--winner            - Winner's slot (during reveal/complete)\nlotr-hwheel__slot-container          - Slot content wrapper\nlotr-hwheel__slot-name               - Player name in slot\nlotr-hwheel__avatar                  - Player avatar\nlotr-hwheel__avatar--empty           - Empty slot avatar\nlotr-hwheel__avatar--winner          - Winner avatar highlight\nlotr-hwheel__avatar-placeholder      - Placeholder \"?\" in empty slot\nlotr-hwheel__fade                    - Edge fade effect\nlotr-hwheel__fade--left              - Left fade\nlotr-hwheel__fade--right             - Right fade\nlotr-hwheel__legend                  - Player odds legend\nlotr-hwheel__legend-item             - Legend item (one player)\nlotr-hwheel__legend-item--you        - Current user in legend\nlotr-hwheel__legend-item--winner     - Winner in legend\nlotr-hwheel__legend-name             - Player name in legend\nlotr-hwheel__legend-entries          - Entry count in legend\nlotr-hwheel__legend-prob             - Win probability % in legend\nlotr-hwheel__legend-empty            - \"No players yet\" message\nlotr-hwheel__winner-announce         - Winner announcement box\nlotr-hwheel__win-animation           - Star/coin animation container\nlotr-hwheel__win-stars               - Star burst container\nlotr-hwheel__win-star                - Individual star\nlotr-hwheel__win-coins               - Coin animation container\nlotr-hwheel__win-coin                - Individual coin\nlotr-hwheel__winner-text             - Winner text\nlotr-hwheel__winner-text--you        - \"YOU WON!\" text\n```\n\n### Sidebar\n\n```\nlotr-sidebar                         - Sidebar container\nlotr-sidebar__title                  - \"Current Round\" heading\nlotr-sidebar__game-info              - Game information section\nlotr-sidebar__row                    - Info row (label + value)\nlotr-sidebar__tier                   - Tier name with color\nlotr-sidebar__your-stats             - User stats section\nlotr-sidebar__stat                   - Single stat (entries/odds)\nlotr-sidebar__stat-label             - Stat label\nlotr-sidebar__stat-value             - Stat value\nlotr-sidebar__pot                    - Prize pool amount\nlotr-sidebar__status                 - Round status text\nlotr-sidebar__fairness               - VRF fairness section\nlotr-sidebar__fairness-title         - \"Round Fairness\" heading\nlotr-sidebar__fairness-row           - Fairness info row\nlotr-sidebar__hash                   - Hash display (Round ID/VRF Request)\nlotr-sidebar__hash--revealed         - VRF proof revealed state\nlotr-action-btn                      - Action button (Join/Buy/Connect)\nlotr-claimed-text                    - Claimed payout message\n```\n\n### History Modal\n\n```\nlotr-history-modal                   - History detail modal\nlotr-history-modal__section          - Modal section (Stats/Fairness)\nlotr-history-modal__section-title    - Section heading\nlotr-history-modal__row              - Info row\nlotr-history-modal__highlight        - Highlighted value (pool/payout)\nlotr-history-modal__hash             - Hash display (Round ID/VRF)\nlotr-history-modal__winner--you      - Winner highlight if current user\nlotr-history-modal__verify-link      - Link to fairness page\nlotr-history-result                  - History entry result display\nlotr-history-result__separator       - Separator in result (|)\n```\n\n---\n\n## Key Test Scenarios & CSS Selectors\n\n### Test 1: Load Lobby & Select Tier\n```\nSelector: .lotr-tier-lobby\nState: Initial load shows 6 tier cards\nAction: Click .lotr-tier-card for any tier\nExpected: Card adds .lotr-tier-card--selected class\n```\n\n### Test 2: Join Round\n```\nSelector: .lotr-action-btn (text \"Join Round\")\nAction: Click button\nLoading State: Button shows \"Joining...\" \nExpected: User enters round, sidebar appears with game info\n```\n\n### Test 3: Countdown Phase\n```\nSelector: .lotr-active-round--countdown\nTimer: .lotr-countdown--large shows MM:SS\nTimer Modifiers: \n  - .lotr-countdown--urgent (when <=10 seconds)\n  - .lotr-countdown--final (when <=5 seconds)\nWheel: .lotr-hwheel__strip animates slowly\nAction: Wait for countdown to end\n```\n\n### Test 4: Spinning Phase\n```\nSelector: .lotr-active-round--spinning\nWheel: .lotr-hwheel performs rapid rotation then decelerates\nDuration: ~5 seconds\nAction: System automatically transitions to revealing phase\n```\n\n### Test 5: Winner Reveal\n```\nSelector: .lotr-active-round--revealing or .lotr-active-round--complete\nAnimations:\n  - .lotr-hwheel__winner-announce appears\n  - .lotr-hwheel__win-stars (8 stars) burst outward\n  - .lotr-hwheel__win-coins (6 coins) animate\nWinner Slot:\n  - Winning slot has .lotr-hwheel__slot--winner\n  - Avatar has .lotr-hwheel__avatar--winner\nLegend:\n  - Winner's legend item has .lotr-hwheel__legend-item--winner\n  - Current user's legend item has .lotr-hwheel__legend-item--you\nText:\n  - If current user won: .lotr-hwheel__winner-text--you\n  - Shows \"YOU WON!\" with avatar\n```\n\n### Test 6: Sidebar Verification\n```\nDuring Active Round:\n  - .lotr-sidebar__title shows \"Current Round\"\n  - .lotr-sidebar__tier shows tier name with glowing color\n  - .lotr-sidebar__stat shows \"Your Entries\" and \"Your Odds\"\n  - .lotr-sidebar__fairness shows Round ID, VRF Request, and (after reveal) VRF Proof\n  - .lotr-sidebar__hash--revealed added when VRF proof available\n```\n\n### Test 7: Buy More Entries\n```\nDuring Waiting/Countdown Phase:\n  - .lotr-action-btn shows \"Buy Entry\"\n  - On click, button shows \"Buying...\"\n  - Round updates with new entry count\n  - Wheel visualization updates with new slot\n```\n\n### Test 8: Return to Lobby\n```\nFrom Active Round:\n  - .lotr-tier-round__back button available\n  - Click: removes .lotr-active-round class\n  - Returns to .lotr-tier-lobby\n```\n\n### Test 9: History Modal\n```\nSelector: History entries in game layout (outside lord-of-rngs classes)\nClick on history entry:\n  - .lotr-history-modal appears\n  - .lotr-history-modal__section contains \"Round Stats\" and \"VRF Fairness\"\n  - .lotr-history-modal__highlight for pool/payout amounts\n  - .lotr-history-modal__hash for hash values\n  - .lotr-history-modal__verify-link at bottom\n```\n\n---\n\n## Dynamic Class Patterns\n\n### Phase-Based Classes\nAll phase states generate dynamic classes: `lotr-active-round--{phase}` and `lotr-tier-card--{phase}`\n- Valid phases: `waiting`, `countdown`, `spinning`, `revealing`, `complete`\n\n### Conditional Modifiers\n- `.lotr-countdown--urgent`: Active when `timeLeft <= 10`\n- `.lotr-countdown--final`: Active when `timeLeft <= 5`\n- `.lotr-tier-card--selected`: Active on selected tier\n- `.lotr-hwheel__slot--you`: Current user's slot\n- `.lotr-hwheel__slot--winner`: Winning slot during reveal/complete\n- `.lotr-hwheel__legend-item--you`: Current user in legend\n- `.lotr-hwheel__legend-item--winner`: Winner in legend\n\n### Tier-Specific Gem Icons\n```\n.rng-tier-gem--{tier}\n  - iron, bronze, silver, gold, platinum, diamond\n```\n\n---\n\n## Button Labels & Actions\n\n| Button Class | Label | State | Action |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `.lotr-action-btn` | \"Connect Wallet\" | Not connected | Opens wallet modal |\n| `.lotr-action-btn` | \"Join Round\" | Tier selected, round joinable | Sends join transaction |\n| `.lotr-action-btn` (disabled) | \"Waiting for new round...\" | Tier selected, round in progress | — |\n| `.lotr-action-btn` | \"Buy Entry\" | In active round, phase waiting/countdown | Buys 1 more entry |\n| `.lotr-action-btn` (disabled) | \"RNG Revealing...\" | In active round, phase spinning/revealing | — |\n| `.lotr-action-btn` (disabled) | Payout amount (text) | Winner, phase complete | Shows earned amount |\n\n---\n\n## Sidebar Content Changes by State\n\n### No Round Selected\n- Sidebar hidden\n\n### Tier Selected (Not In Round)\n- Title: \"Current Round\"\n- Shows: Tier, Players, Total Entries, Entry Cost, Prize Pool\n- Shows: Your Entries (if you've entered), Your Odds\n- Shows: Join/Connection buttons\n- Shows: VRF Fairness section\n\n### In Active Round\n- Title: \"Current Round\"\n- Shows: Tier, Players, Total Entries, Entry Cost, Prize Pool, Status\n- Shows: Your Entries, Your Odds\n- Shows: Buy Entry or Status button (varies by phase)\n- Shows: Full VRF Fairness (Round ID, VRF Request, VRF Proof after reveal)\n\n---\n\n## Animation & Timing Details\n\n| Event | Duration | CSS Classes | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| Wheel slow scroll | Continuous | `.lotr-hwheel__strip` | During waiting/countdown |\n| Countdown timer | Real-time | `.lotr-countdown--{size} {modifiers}` | Updates every 100ms |\n| Spin animation | ~5000ms | `.lotr-hwheel` | 3 full loops + deceleration |\n| Star burst | Simultaneous with spin | `.lotr-hwheel__win-star` | 8 stars, CSS animation |\n| Coin animation | Simultaneous with spin | `.lotr-hwheel__win-coin` | 6 coins, CSS animation |\n| Auto-return (non-winner) | 3000ms after complete | — | Auto-closes round view |\n| Auto-return (winner) | 5000ms after claim | — | Auto-closes round view |\n\n---\n\n## Assertion Examples for E2E Tests\n\n```typescript\n// Check tier lobby is displayed\nawait expect(page.locator('.lotr-tier-lobby')).toBeVisible();\n\n// Check tier card is selected\nawait expect(page.locator('.lotr-tier-card--selected')).toBeVisible();\n\n// Check sidebar appears with round info\nawait expect(page.locator('.lotr-sidebar__title')).toContainText('Current Round');\n\n// Check action button text\nawait expect(page.locator('.lotr-action-btn')).toContainText('Join Round');\n\n// Check countdown is urgent (<=10 seconds)\nawait expect(page.locator('.lotr-countdown--urgent')).toBeVisible();\n\n// Check wheel is spinning\nawait expect(page.locator('.lotr-active-round--spinning')).toBeVisible();\n\n// Check winner announcement\nawait expect(page.locator('.lotr-hwheel__winner-announce')).toBeVisible();\n\n// Check current user's slot highlighted\nawait expect(page.locator('.lotr-hwheel__slot--you')).toBeVisible();\n\n// Check winning slot highlighted\nawait expect(page.locator('.lotr-hwheel__slot--winner')).toBeVisible();\n\n// Check legend shows current user\nawait expect(page.locator('.lotr-hwheel__legend-item--you')).toBeVisible();\n\n// Check sidebar status\nawait expect(page.locator('.lotr-sidebar__status')).toContainText('Countdown!');\n\n// Check history modal opened\nawait expect(page.locator('.lotr-history-modal')).toBeVisible();\n```\n\n---\n\nThis comprehensive guide should enable you to write reliable, specific E2E tests targeting all Lord of the RNGs UI states and interactions."}],"totalDurationMs":99369,"totalTokens":65738,"totalToolUseCount":30,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":218,"cache_read_input_tokens":60682,"output_tokens":4838,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":218,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
