{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01KRWvbi3TRHttzx9g4e2FfY","type":"tool_result","content":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/lordofrngs/src/instructions/start_spin.rs:    /// Orao randomness account (created by Orao CPI).\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/lordofrngs/src/instructions/start_spin.rs:    /// CHECK: Orao VRF CPI validates and initializes this account.\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/lordofrngs/src/instructions/start_spin.rs:    pub orao_random: UncheckedAccount<'info>,\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/lordofrngs/src/instructions/start_spin.rs:    // Request Orao VRF — use round PDA key as unique seed\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/lordofrngs/src/instructions/start_spin.rs:        &ctx.accounts.orao_random.to_account_info(),\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/lordofrngs/src/instructions/start_spin.rs:    round.vrf_request_key = ctx.accounts.orao_random.key();\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/lordofrngs/src/instructions/claim_payout.rs:    let randomness = read_orao_randomness(&ctx.accounts.randomness_account)?;\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/lordofrngs/src/instructions/timeout_refund.rs:    let vrf_is_fulfilled = read_orao_randomness(&ctx.accounts.randomness_account)\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/src/instructions/claim_payout.rs:    let randomness = read_orao_randomness(&ctx.accounts.randomness_account)?;\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/src/instructions/timeout_cancel.rs:    let vrf_is_fulfilled = read_orao_randomness(&ctx.accounts.randomness_account)\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/src/instructions/join_match.rs:    /// Orao randomness account (created by Orao CPI).\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-u